public class Feature
extends DefinedTermBase

Individual property of observed phenomena able to be described or measured. Experts do not use the word feature for the actual description but only for the property itself. Naming this class FeatureType would create confusion. NEEDS TO BE COMPLEMENTED SPM / TDWG http://rs.tdwg. org/ontology/voc/SpeciesProfileModel
